{"tid":1383744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［前線&金主唔想死就入黎］全世界同我玩遠攻","createTime":"2019-07-29T18:16:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T16:35:14.000Z","uid":69221,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e116cddbe193904c0a454a3c84f62b1b4f44cf5a","tid":1383744,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:16:31.000Z","msg":"泛民左膠又岀黎叫散水啦，又岀黎引人送頭呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GtgRm9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GtgRm9.png&h=8e4ba17a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">現場同網上都開始有人有組織引導啲行動去返雨傘失敗模式</span><br />\n俾人擊潰就散水，唔撚係叫 be water<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真正be water係hit and run<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你冇遠攻，只係被動防守<br />\n變左大量嘅人力成本只係用黎佔路，效率極低。<br />\n對方唔郁你冇得郁，行行企企唔知做乜<br />\n一衝擊就更危險，容易落單俾人捉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解鬼佬連農場係用噴漆唔係用memo紙？<br />\n因為高效率呀，噴一噴就成幅牆人哋又難清<br />\n同理，點解人地革命係用磚頭係用火？<br />\n因為係暴徒呀，岀黎搗亂，係俾人捉果個呀<br />\n<br />\n緊係拉遠距離打啦，弓又好投石索又好<br />\n點都好過拎住防具衝上前<br />\n又冇隊型，輸硬又容易俾人捉<br />\n<br />\n好多人玩過雨傘online，見啲左膠做乜又跟住做<br />\n拎住遮排排企，又冇遠攻喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />企喺度等人打你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣有用，隻game就唔會執柒左啦<br />\n<br />\n最重要係到今時今日左膠都用緊同一招「好危險呀<br />\n一陣前面退唔到呀，我好擔心有人會受傷呀」要拆左一邊路障，你又阻唔到<br />\n變左跟本防到車防唔到人，重點係咩呀，你咁辛苦起岀黎，人地用刀仔就拆到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />完全反智<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以後整路障，應該係路中間堆座山岀黎，點火<br />\n咁就癱瘓左條路，要恢復交通起碼要消防岀手<br />\n咁熱，你叫狗仔點拆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">然後</span><br />\n<br />\n<em>［領取新手村武器］</em><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HSrBRiN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHSrBRiN.png&h=d9e000ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RzDMCVdPwnE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRzDMCVdPwnE&d=BhuSHdI33QWLqsaIYsxmJTBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=be760683\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RzDMCVdPwnE</a><br />\n<br />\n一個人射又得，叫埋兩個兄弟射又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n射完撚完狗就<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">即刻走</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">永遠保持距離</span><br />\n<br />\n人多就去第二度再玩過，一樣起路障，唔洗守！要令到狗冇辦法包圍<br />\n<br />\n玩到就天黑，人少見唔對路就返屋企<br />\n<br />\n冇事先做到世界冠軍咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a709b27aba7eddb7d85ed2c77d6ad1844474cbfd","tid":1383744,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:17:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b27d6407166978661b4d6d18869dff9998e2b6de","tid":1383744,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:18:22.000Z","msg":"睇晒佢"},{"pid":"ca1c77f9e391cfe2c22cf408a3667bc62acd5984","tid":1383744,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:21:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85b1d36a1e6c9f0d180fe90560468af1ab8bd034","tid":1383744,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:23:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56336195bbdad58c1f537f1a090f25ef77b99b84","tid":1383744,"uid":259613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:25:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1kWLdD8Vc7s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D1kWLdD8Vc7s&d=BhuSHdI33QWLqsaIYsxmJTBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=ffae7778\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.yout